query:
INSERT INTO alertSettings (tentId, alertsEnabled, tempEnabled, rhEnabled, ppfdEnabled) 
SELECT id, true, true, true, true 
FROM tents 
WHERE id NOT IN (SELECT tentId FROM alertSettings);
